data.message: Mentioning Tatham, this sessio (by him) is great http://blog.tatham.oddie.com.au/2012/12/17/new-talk-your-website-is-in-production-its-broken-now-what/

It always makes me laugh because I worked on the codebase from which most of these tips were originated for several months, so whenever he says something like "a large auctions website here in Australia" I just can't help smiling :)
